seo: 域名反查,爱站权重,批量主域
seo_en: domain reverse lookup,Aizhan weight,batch main domain
summary: 该插件通过输入的字符串自动匹配域名中的主域，并通过爱站接口反查域名权重，筛选出权重大于0的域名。
summary_en: This plugin automatically matches the main domain in the input string and reverses the domain weight through the Aizhan interface, filtering out domains with a weight greater than 0.
